  "0_text" : "<strong>Hi there!</strong><br><br>Your contribution in this application will help us in cell biology research. Your collaboration is truly meaningful, since you play a key role as important as the scientists do. Through advanced optical microscopy, the experiment being carried out works on the search for drugs to help in Cancer's treatments. Namely, the research is focused in finding proper drugs to induce apoptosis, a type of cell death.<br><br><strong>We want to sincere thank you for your participation!</strong><br><br>",
  "2_text_1" : "The application is divided in several steps. In the left part of that bar you can find the question to be answered at the current step. ",
