  "3_text" : "This is the most important part. On the left the image to be analyzed is displayed. That is the one whose channel can be changed. Below it, the response area is placed containing the forms that change in every step. On the right, samples of every step are displayed.<br><br>",
  "4_text_1" : "The progress bar shows the step in which you are at any time highlighting it in white. It is made up of nine parts, since nine are the steps to be done.<br><br>To move from one step to the other one, you can either use the two arrows at the sides of the bar, ",
